This package requires python (>2.5) and pyglet (http://www.pyglet.org/).

If your running this script on a Mac, there is a bug in pyglet with newer
versions of Snow Leopard 64 bit, i.e.
  http://code.google.com/p/pyglet/issues/detail?id=438

Therefore you must add the following environment variable (before running any
of the scripts/unit tests).
  export VERSIONER_PYTHON_PREFER_32_BIT=yes

